# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Proprietary firmware binary (DO NOT COMMIT — see README "Reproducing the analysis")
# The WPM Primus firmware is proprietary. Do not redistribute the binary.
# Use scripts/fetch_firmware.sh to pull it from the public OTA endpoint; it saves
# into firmware_binary/ (NOT firmware/, which holds our open-source ESPHome code).
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
*.bin
!ghidra_scripts/**/*.java
KD360X_OTA_*.bin
firmware_binary/

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Large / regeneratable analysis artifacts
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Extracted firmware segments (regenerated by scripts/extract_segments.py)
analysis/extracted/
# Raw string dumps (regenerated)
analysis/strings_seg*.txt
# Ghidra project (29 MB, regeneratable from the binary + scripts)
ghidra_project/

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Ghidra analysis output (large, regeneratable via ghidra_scripts/)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
ghidra_out/

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Python
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
.Python
.venv/
venv/
env/

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# PlatformIO / Arduino (for the future open-source firmware)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
.pio/
.pioenvs/
.piolibdeps/
.vscode/
*.elf
*.map

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# ESPHome firmware build artifacts
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
.venv/
venv/
firmware/.esphome/          # ESPHome build/cache dir
firmware/secrets.yaml       # real WiFi creds — never commit
# Icon font source — 15MB, ESPHome subsets it at compile time.
# Fetched by scripts/fetch_fonts.sh (called from run_sim.sh). Keep .gitkeep only.
firmware/fonts/*.ttf
/esphome_build/

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Editor / OS
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Misc temp
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
_seed.bin
*.log
